                        <interp inst="t18390812-name-156" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS JUKES</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the prosecutors' employ—Mr. Freeman spoke to me—I saw the prisoner take the pewter out of the ladle and conceal it in his clothes, where it was afterwards found.</p>
